subject: NCAA Basketball Championships (Men)
Basketball (College)
lead_paragraph: No. 12 Oregon could not get by Louisville’s full-court press, so the Ducks just stopped trying. The top-seeded Cardinals held the Ducks to 45 percent shooting.
